1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 20=

4
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,719
At the Martial Arts Assembly,

5
00:00:22,719 --> 00:00:24,440
everyone swore they'd destroy

6
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:25,320
the Demon Sect.

7
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:26,480
And look who actually showed up.

8
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:27,559
A bunch of old men and weaklings.

9
00:00:27,839 --> 00:00:29,320
Even the leaders of the major sects

10
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:30,839
all found excuses not to come.

11
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,320
So we risk our lives,

12
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,520
and they take all the glory?

13
00:00:33,759 --> 00:00:34,679
You've been nagging

14
00:00:34,679 --> 00:00:35,960
the whole way here.

15
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:36,840
Will you ever stop?

16
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:38,039
Keep it up,

17
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:39,960
and I don't know
if we'll kill any of them,

18
00:00:40,039 --> 00:00:40,880
but you'll talk me to death.

19
00:00:41,119 --> 00:00:42,119
That's your problem.

20
00:00:42,119 --> 00:00:43,039
Like I'd care.

21
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:45,280
I never expected
much help from them anyway.

22
00:00:45,399 --> 00:00:46,960
At least they make us look stronger.

23
00:00:49,079 --> 00:00:51,200
Liuchu Manor is just ahead,
at the foot of the mountain.

24
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:52,280
Anything unusual?

25
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,280
The gates are shut tight.

26
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:54,399
The trees inside block our view.

27
00:00:54,399 --> 00:00:55,359
We can't tell what's going on.

28
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:59,039
Here's the plan.
I'll take some men in first.

29
00:00:59,039 --> 00:01:00,079
The rest of you wait here.

30
00:01:00,359 --> 00:01:01,479
Once I fight my way inside,

31
00:01:01,479 --> 00:01:02,280
come in and back me up.

32
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:02,719
No.

33
00:01:04,079 --> 00:01:05,680
Master Baiyi chose Liuchu Manor
for this meeting.

34
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,599
He must have something planned.

35
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:07,959
If we rush in,

36
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,159
we'll be at a disadvantage

37
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:09,959
and at his mercy.

38
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,359
But we're already here.

39
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:12,879
We can't stand around forever.

40
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,159
How about this?

41
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:17,680
Ms. Duan, you keep everyone here.

42
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,000
I'll go in alone.

43
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,280
Once I know what's inside,

44
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,280
I'll send a signal.

45
00:01:21,439 --> 00:01:23,200
Then bring everyone in to back me up.

46
00:01:23,239 --> 00:01:24,560
No. It's too dangerous.

47
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,040
What if Master Baiyi is inside?

48
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:27,519
You'd be walking straight into a trap.

49
00:01:27,519 --> 00:01:28,760
Someone has to act as bait

50
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:29,879
and find out what's inside.

51
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:30,879
- But...
- No more buts.

52
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,680
Feng, Ziting,

53
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:34,079
keep everyone on the mountain.

54
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:35,079
Don't make a move

55
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,079
until you see my signal.

56
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:49,519
Xiao, stay here with our disciples.

57
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,599
I'm going in to investigate.

58
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,799
Understood. Be careful, Miss.

59
00:02:04,180 --> 00:02:09,460
(Liuchu Manor)

60
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:17,140
(Liuchu Manor)

61
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:19,500
(Liuchu Manor)

62
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:28,159
Why does Liuchu Manor
look like a pleasure house?

63
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,560
Did we come to the wrong place?

64
00:02:33,479 --> 00:02:35,120
Honored guests,

65
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,080
you've had a long journey.

66
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,879
Our master has prepared a feast
to welcome you.

67
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:39,000
This way, please.

68
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:50,280
(Zhenqu Pavilion)

69
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:58,439
Please enjoy yourselves.

70
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,199
Our master will be here shortly.

71
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:35,240
There's more to Liuchu Manor
than meets the eye.

72
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,319
Zhenqu Pavilion is hidden inside.

73
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:40,639
Why haven't I sensed any danger
since we came in?

74
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:43,599
Still, something feels off.

75
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,000
Stay sharp.

76
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,599
Mr. Peng, it's been a while.

77
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,800
Ever since we parted
at the flower carriage,

78
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,840
I've thought of you every day.

79
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,599
It's been a long time.

80
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,720
We haven't heard a thing.

81
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:18,759
Do you think they've run into trouble?

82
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:19,360
Ms. Mu,

83
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,319
don't worry.

84
00:04:20,319 --> 00:04:21,439
With Dasheng's skills,

85
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:22,439
whatever trouble they run into,

86
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:23,639
he'll know what to do.

87
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,040
Right?

88
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,639
Besides, Ms. Duan is with him.

89
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,040
They'll be fine.

90
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,279
If I didn't have disciples to lead,

91
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:30,879
I'd have gone with her already.

92
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,680
I wouldn't be standing here like a fool.

93
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:35,120
Ms. Mu is right.

94
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,319
Unlike some people,

95
00:04:36,319 --> 00:04:37,319
who are all talk

96
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:37,920
and no action.

97
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,000
Pretty boy, who are you talking about?

98
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,920
Whoever answered.

99
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,360
Come fight me!

100
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,040
Enough!

101
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:44,079
Keep arguing,
and I'll sew your mouths shut.

102
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,000
What are you laughing at?

103
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,360
The last time we met,

104
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,360
you had

105
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,439
a sweet young woman by your side.

106
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:00,920
And now there's a bold,

107
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:03,680
fiery swordswoman by your side instead.

108
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:07,120
You seem so kind and honest,

109
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,920
but you win a woman's heart
only to walk away.

110
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,000
What are you talking about?

111
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,879
Submit to the Master,

112
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,519
and you'll have your pick of women.

113
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,680
Then tell me

114
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,319
what your master

115
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,040
wants you to say.

116
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:28,639
The sects are all out for themselves,

117
00:05:28,639 --> 00:05:29,720
and corruption is everywhere.

118
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:32,319
Sir, you're exceptionally gifted.

119
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:35,079
Surely you don't want
to stoop to their level.

120
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:38,319
The Master can clear your path to power,

121
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,720
unite the martial world,

122
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,319
and make you

123
00:05:41,319 --> 00:05:43,720
its undisputed ruler.

124
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,639
What do you want in return?

125
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,480
It's simple.

126
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:51,319
Swear your loyalty to him

127
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,920
and take him as your master.

128
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,199
Then the martial world will be at peace,

129
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:56,720
and all this fighting will end.

130
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,199
So your master

131
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:04,399
wants me to become

132
00:06:04,399 --> 00:06:06,839
a puppet who does whatever he says.

133
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:09,519
You misunderstand, Mr. Peng.

134
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,519
With my master's power,

135
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:14,439
uniting the martial world
is only a matter of time.

136
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,120
He wants to put you in power

137
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,519
because he recognizes your talent

138
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:19,879
and is eager to have you on his side.

139
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:27,199
Does your master know

140
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,800
I'm dying?

141
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,920
I have less than a month left.

142
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:36,720
Sir, do you really believe
you were born with sealed meridians

143
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,480
and are doomed to die?

144
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,199
What do you know?

145
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,920
The Master said

146
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:47,439
your life
was never meant to end so soon.

147
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,839
If you submit to him,

148
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:53,279
he can heal your sealed meridians

149
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,680
and give you a life of wealth and power.

150
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:56,319
Who exactly is your master?

151
00:06:57,079 --> 00:07:00,319
I'd like to know even more than you do.

152
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:03,800
I've been at Zhenqu Pavilion
since I was fourteen,

153
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,800
and I've never seen his face.

154
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,319
Accept the Master's offer,

155
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,600
and you'll rule

156
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,480
the entire martial world

157
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:14,240
and escape your cursed fate.

158
00:07:14,839 --> 00:07:16,399
Tell me,

159
00:07:16,439 --> 00:07:18,720
what better deal could there be?

160
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:20,920
It does

161
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,120
sound tempting.

162
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:26,279
So you'll accept?

163
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,480
Quite the opposite.

164
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,279
Peng Dasheng,

165
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,519
do you know what happens
to those who refuse the Master?

166
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,920
They die.

167
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,920
I'm dying anyway.

168
00:07:38,279 --> 00:07:39,560
If I can settle the score

169
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,120
with my enemy before I die,

170
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,639
I'd call that a win.

171
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,800
You don't know what's good for you.

172
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,120
Then don't blame me.

173
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,440
At this rate,

174
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,519
we won't last much longer.

175
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,039
Haven't you noticed?

176
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:42,039
The other guests don't seem
to notice us.

177
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,120
That's strange.

178
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,720
I'll draw their attention.

179
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:50,840
Move when you get the chance.

180
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:57,080
With skills like that, you've got
no business playing the zither.

181
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,720
Go home and teach children instead.

182
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:15,240
Ms. Mu, I know you're worried,

183
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,320
but try to stay calm.

184
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,480
That's right, Ms. Mu.

185
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,679
Without you,

186
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:20,080
no one can lead the Wudu Sect disciples.

187
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,480
If the Demon Sect breaks through,

188
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,080
we won't know what to do.

189
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,519
Wudu Sect disciples, hear my command!

190
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,360
Yes!

191
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:30,200
From now on, follow Mr. Tang's orders.

192
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,399
Understood?

193
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:33,320
No, no. I can't do that.

194
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,240
Ms. Mu,

195
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:36,320
the Wudu Sect has more rules
than the Tang Clan has hidden weapons.

196
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:38,480
I'm an outsider.
I can't order them around.

197
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,399
You say no to everything.

198
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:41,519
Then what do you suggest?

199
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:42,679
I'll go.

200
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,679
I'll slip into the manor
and see what's happening.

201
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:46,320
Wait for my signal before coming in.

202
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:47,840
You?

203
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,240
Can you handle it?

204
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,559
Don't worry, Ms. Mu.

205
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:54,360
I may not win a fight,

206
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,679
but no one beats me

207
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:57,159
at running away.

208
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,320
(If he gets all the credit
for destroying the Demon Sect,)

209
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,919
(the Tang Clan will have come
all this way for nothing.)

210
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:11,120
Those two fools really are
made for each other.

211
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,679
Are you okay?

212
00:11:05,679 --> 00:11:06,480
I'm fine.

213
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,200
Peng Dasheng,

214
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,320
don't tell me you're backing down.

215
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:17,840
What now?

216
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:24,380
(Wine)

217
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,799
We'll have to risk it.

218
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,720
Ms. Su, of all things,

219
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:59,879
why mess with grave goods?

220
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:02,000
Aren't you afraid
they'll bring bad luck?

221
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:05,039
How did you see through
my Linglong Illusion Technique?

222
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:07,240
When Ms. Duan
slashed that woman's throat,

223
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,600
not a drop of blood came out.

224
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:11,399
That's when I knew
none of them were real.

225
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:15,679
We must've entered your illusion

226
00:12:15,679 --> 00:12:17,320
the moment we heard the music
after we came in.

227
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:20,000
Everything we've seen and heard since
has been false.

228
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,440
You saw through the illusion,

229
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:24,840
but how did you know
fire was its weakness?

230
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,720
Five Elements illusions
draw on yin energy.

231
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,480
They need moisture to take form

232
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:30,080
and can't withstand fire.

233
00:12:30,519 --> 00:12:33,840
The running water in this courtyard

234
00:12:34,639 --> 00:12:37,519
must be sustaining
the illusion formation

235
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,480
and clouding people's minds.

236
00:12:41,279 --> 00:12:43,120
You're every bit as clever
as I expected.

237
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,840
I'm impressed.

238
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:49,919
But my illusions
have never harmed anyone.

239
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:53,519
I merely turn people's greed, anger,
obsession, and resentment

240
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:56,200
back on them.

241
00:12:56,519 --> 00:12:57,320
Su Yeye,

242
00:12:57,919 --> 00:12:59,960
you use Zhenqu Pavilion's reputation
as a pleasure house

243
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,120
to lure martial artists here.

244
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:03,639
Then you ensnare them with illusions

245
00:13:03,879 --> 00:13:05,320
and force them to serve you,

246
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,320
tearing countless families apart.

247
00:13:08,879 --> 00:13:09,919
After using such dirty tricks,

248
00:13:09,919 --> 00:13:11,600
you still claim
you've never deceived anyone?

249
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:16,120
Quite the sharp tongue, little lady.

250
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:19,600
But do you really think
breaking my illusion formation

251
00:13:19,639 --> 00:13:22,000
means you'll leave here unharmed?

252
00:13:39,900 --> 00:13:40,380
♪Come on♪

253
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:45,580
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

254
00:13:47,540 --> 00:13:50,500
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

255
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:53,700
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

256
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:56,780
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

257
00:13:57,180 --> 00:13:59,780
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

258
00:14:00,300 --> 00:14:03,260
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

259
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:06,500
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

260
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:09,580
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

261
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:12,500
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

262
00:14:13,060 --> 00:14:16,380
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

263
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:19,420
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

264
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:25,100
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

265
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:27,540
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

266
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:30,620
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

267
00:14:31,340 --> 00:14:33,740
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

268
00:14:33,860 --> 00:14:37,540
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

269
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:40,260
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

270
00:14:41,180 --> 00:14:43,300
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

271
00:14:43,460 --> 00:14:46,740
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

272
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:51,060
♪I am my own king♪

273
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:05,700
♪I emerge into the world♪

274
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:07,460
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

275
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:08,820
♪My pride is my trump card♪

276
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,620
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

277
00:15:10,620 --> 00:15:12,020
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

278
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:13,780
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

279
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:15,300
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

280
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:17,020
♪I dare to break every rule♪

281
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:18,340
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

282
00:15:18,340 --> 00:15:20,180
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

283
00:15:20,180 --> 00:15:21,420
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

284
00:15:21,420 --> 00:15:23,660
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

285
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:25,180
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

286
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:26,780
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

287
00:15:26,780 --> 00:15:28,380
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

288
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:30,100
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

289
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:31,820
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

290
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:33,180
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

291
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:34,820
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

292
00:15:34,820 --> 00:15:36,300
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

293
00:15:36,300 --> 00:15:38,020
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

294
00:15:38,020 --> 00:15:39,620
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

295
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:41,180
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

296
00:15:41,180 --> 00:15:45,500
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

297
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:47,660
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

298
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:50,260
♪Let me write the legend♪

299
00:15:55,140 --> 00:15:57,700
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

300
00:15:57,700 --> 00:16:01,020
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

301
00:16:01,020 --> 00:16:03,500
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

302
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:07,580
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

303
00:16:07,940 --> 00:16:10,540
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

304
00:16:10,660 --> 00:16:13,020
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

305
00:16:13,020 --> 00:16:16,060
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

306
00:16:16,060 --> 00:16:21,100
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
